Title: UW-Madison InterVarsity Graduate Christian Fellowship
Body: Date: Mon, 04 Nov 1996 23:45:21 GMT Server: NCSA/1.4.2 Content-type: text/html Last-modified: Mon, 04 Nov 1996 16:14:33 GMT Content-length: 2345 UW-Madison InterVarsity Graduate Christian Fellowship InterVarsity Graduate Christian Fellowship University of Wisconsin-Madison UW's InterVarsity Graduate Christian Fellowship is a chapter of InterVarsity Christian Fellowship's Graduate Student Ministry whose vision is to build Christian graduate student fellowships which develop biblical disciples and engage the univerity in all its ethnic, social and academic diversity with the Gospel of Jesus Christ.
